node.text:
A collection of moments captured last winter during my time on assignment in Western Greenland, a place so profoundly beautiful but yet alarmingly fragile. 
Location: Greenland - Uummannaq, Saattut, Illussiat.

Music: Icarus by Dexter Britain.

Shot on @sonyalpha.anz A7riii @djiglobal Mavic 2 Pro 
@visitgreenland

Moments captured - Patagonia 2017

EXCITING ANNOUNCEMENT:

My good friends at @willandbear have just launched an incredible content creaters competition with a chance to WIN 5k CASH + SONY CAMERA

Photographers, storytellers, filmmakers, and picture takers of every description, in any place. We invite you to share your moments captured for the chance to win!

Enter now to win 10k worth of prizes. Score 5k cash + a @sonyalpha.anz Alpha 7C + 29-60mm kit lens + Master Class with @stefan_haworth 

Entries open worldwide! The contest closed at midnight on 21st Sept AEST. Full T&C's on the entry page. 
@willandbear

node.text:
Flying over the sprawling textures of the Norman River & seasonal flood plains of the Gulf of Carpentaria. It was a true feast for the eyes attempting to capture & untangle the labyrinth of intricate patterns that laid out as we hurled through the air high above. A scene forever etched in my memory..

@queensland #thisisqueensland
